# Cursor Rules — Astro Starseed

## Stack

- Astro 5 (hybrid rendering) + React 19 islands
- Tailwind CSS 4 with OKLch design tokens
- shadcn/ui (Radix primitives) in `src/components/ui/`
- Framer Motion 12 for animations
- TypeScript strict mode
- pnpm as the only package manager (Node 22.x)

## Rules

### General
- Use `pnpm` exclusively — never `npm` or `yarn`.
- All TypeScript must be strictly typed — no `any`.
- Run `pnpm format` (Prettier) before committing.

### Components
- `.astro` files for static/layout content.
- `.tsx` files for interactive React islands — always add a client directive (`client:load`, `client:visible`, `client:idle`).
- shadcn/ui primitives live in `src/components/ui/` — add via `pnpm dlx shadcn add <component>`, do NOT edit manually.
- Custom components go directly in `src/components/`.

### Styling
- Use `cn()` from `src/lib/utils.ts` for all conditional class merging (clsx + tailwind-merge).
- Never use raw hex colors. All colors must use CSS variables defined in `src/styles/global.css`.
- Design tokens are OKLch CSS variables on `:root` and `.dark` — extend there, not inline.

### Configuration & metadata
- Import site-wide metadata from `src/site.config.ts` — never hardcode strings like site name or URL.
- Astro config (integrations, i18n, output) is in `astro.config.mjs`.

### i18n
- Translation keys go in `src/i18n/locales/<lang>.json`.
- Use helpers from `src/i18n/ui.ts`: `useTranslations()`, `getLangFromUrl()`, `getLocalizedPath()`.
- Default locale `en` has no URL prefix.

### Testing
- E2E tests use Playwright, located in `tests/`.
- Run: `pnpm test:e2e` (headless) or `pnpm test:e2e:ui` (interactive).
- Dev server must be running at `http://localhost:4321` before running tests.
